Daryl Ng

Running Server:
./server <port #>
-automatically assigns port # if unspecified

Running Client:
./cclient <client_name> <server_ip> <port #>

Chat Commands:
All commands work with lowercase.

%M destination-client [text]
-sends a message to one client
NOTE: currently broken but can easily use %C code to fix.

%B [text]
-broadcasts message to all clients

%C num-clients destination-client [destination-client] [text]
-sends message to multiple clients

%L
-lists all clients connected to the server

%E
-exit command